items.title: Indians 3, Royals 2, 10 innings: One Strike From a Streak’s End, Cleveland Indians Rally to Win 22nd Straight
items.summary: The Indians surpassed the 1935 Chicago Cubs for the longest winning streak in the last 101 seasons and are now four short of the major league record, held by the 1916 New York Giants.
